title: Agent Development Kit Deep Dive
description: From Initialization to Ideation to Prompting to Deployment. All of these and the intermediate steps will be covered in the creation of your own Agent application. We all know about AI, but this is much more than that, it is making sure the AI is deployed and available in the most consistent way possible with all the requirements for application development including version control, testing and scaling being covered. You will be given credits to follow along on the workshop.
